1:07:31.958 --> 1:07:34.833
<i>So I think he's probably lurking,
you know,</i>

1:07:34.833 --> 1:07:36.833
<i>fishing for secrets,</i>

1:07:37.458 --> 1:07:40.416
and I bet he's not going to them.
