he'll get caught that way. So he's using...

1:07:44.125 --> 1:07:47.250
<i>blackmail to make them come to him.</i>

1:07:50.791 --> 1:07:51.958
Jesus, John.

1:07:53.875 --> 1:07:54.791
All of them?

1:07:54.791 --> 1:07:56.166
<i>Yeah, no, all of them</i>,

1:07:56.750 --> 1:08:02.125
