1:08:16.041 --> 1:08:18.541
He's... [sighs] He's a parasite.

1:08:19.208 --> 1:08:20.750
<i>He's feeding off it.</i>

1:08:27.541 --> 1:08:29.833
He's on Millfield Avenue SE1.

